msgid "# `pgroonga-primary-maintainer.sh` command"
msgstr "# `pgroonga-primary-maintainer.sh` コマンド"

msgid "Since 3.2.1."
msgstr "3.2.1で追加"

msgid "## Notices"
msgstr "## お知らせ"

msgid ""
"If PostgreSQL is 15 or higher, please use [the "
"`pgroonga_wal_resource_manager` module][pgroonga-wal-resource-manager]. "
"Using that module is a better way to suppress the size of the WAL."
msgstr ""
"PostgreSQL 15以上であれば[`pgroonga_wal_resource_manager`モジュール]"
"[pgroonga-wal-resource-manager]をご利用ください。そのモジュールを利用するほう"
"がより良い方法でおすすめです。"

msgid "## Summary"
msgstr "## 概要"

msgid ""
"`pgroonga-primary-maintainer.sh` command runs `REINDEX INDEX CONCURRENTLY` "
"on indexes for which PGroonga's WAL size exceeds the threshold."
msgstr ""
"`pgroonga-primary-maintainer.sh`コマンドはPGroongaのWALのサイズがしきい値を超"
"えたインデックスに対して、`REINDEX INDEX CONCURRENTLY` を実行します。"

msgid ""
"The purpose is to suppress the size of the WAL on primary servers that have "
"WAL enabled (set `pgroonga.enable_wal = yes`)."
msgstr ""
"このコマンドを実行することで、WALが有効になっている(`pgroonga.enable_wal = "
"yes`が設定されている)プライマリーサーバーにおいてWALのサイズの肥大化を防ぐこ"
"とができます。"

msgid "Notes:"
msgstr "注意:"

msgid ""
"* This command is assumes to run in primary, so do not run it in standby."
msgstr ""
"* このコマンドはプライマリーで動かすことを前提としているため、スタンバイでは"
"実行しないでください。"

msgid ""
"* This command assumes periodic execution, so please use [`pgroonga-generate-"
"primary-maintainer-service.sh` command][generate-primary-maintainer-service] "
"and [`pgroonga-generate-primary-maintainer-timer.sh` command][generate-"
"primary-maintainer-timer]  to set up periodic execution."
msgstr ""
"* このコマンドは定期実行することを前提としているため、[`pgroonga-generate-"
"primary-maintainer-service.sh`マンド][generate-primary-maintainer-service]と"
"[`pgroonga-generate-primary-maintainer-timer.sh`コマンド][generate-primary-"
"maintainer-timer]を使って定期実行の設定をしてください。"

msgid "## Usage"
msgstr "## 使い方"

msgid ""
"```\n"
"pgroonga-primary-maintainer.sh --threshold REINDEX_THRESHOLD_SIZE [--psql "
"PSQL_COMMAND_PATH]"
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Options:\n"
"-t, --threshold:\n"
"  If the specified value is exceeded, `REINDEX INDEX CONCURRENTLY` is run.\n"
"  Specify by size.\n"
"  Example: --threshold 10M, -t 1G\n"
"-c, --psql:\n"
"  Specify the path to `psql` command.\n"
"-h, --help:\n"
"  Display help text and exit."
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Connection information such as `dbname` should be set in environment "
"variables.\n"
"See also: https://www.postgresql.org/docs/current/libpq-envars.html\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

msgid "* `--threshold` option"
msgstr "* `--threshold` オプション"

msgid ""
"  * If the size of WAL exceeds the specified value,, `REINDEX INDEX "
"CONCURRENTLY` is run"
msgstr ""
"  * `REINDEX INDEX CONCURRENTLY` を実行するWALサイズのしきい値を指定します"

msgid "* `--psql` option"
msgstr "* `--psql` オプション"

msgid ""
"  * If `psql` command is installed in a custom path, specify the path for "
"`psql` command"
msgstr "  * `psql` コマンドのパスを指定します"

msgid "* Environment variable"
msgstr "* 環境変数"

msgid "  * Specify connection information to DB in environment variables"
msgstr "  * DBへの接続情報などは環境変数で指定します"

msgid ""
"  * [PostgreSQL Environment Variables][postgresql-environment-variables]"
msgstr "  * [PostgreSQLの環境変数][postgresql-environment-variables]"

msgid "## Example"
msgstr "## 実行例"

msgid ""
"Here is an example of configuring the systemd timer in [`pgroonga-generate-"
"primary-maintainer-service.sh` command][generate-primary-maintainer-service] "
"and [`pgroonga-generate-primary-maintainer-timer.sh` command][generate-"
"primary-maintainer-timer] for use in a periodic execution."
msgstr ""
"[`pgroonga-generate-primary-maintainer-service.sh`コマンド][generate-primary-"
"maintainer-service]と[`pgroonga-generate-primary-maintainer-timer.sh`コマン"
"ド][generate-primary-maintainer-timer]で定期実行の設定をした例です。"

msgid ""
"See [`pgroonga-generate-primary-maintainer-service.sh` command][generate-"
"primary-maintainer-service] and [`pgroonga-generate-primary-maintainer-timer."
"sh` command][generate-primary-maintainer-timer] for details on creating a "
"configuration file."
msgstr ""
"[`pgroonga-generate-primary-maintainer-service.sh`コマンド][generate-primary-"
"maintainer-service]と[`pgroonga-generate-primary-maintainer-timer.sh`コマン"
"ド][generate-primary-maintainer-timer]についてはリンク先を参照してください。"

msgid ""
"In this example, it was specified with `--threshold 20K`. This is the size "
"at which REINDEX will run if `last_block >= 2`."
msgstr ""
"この例ではしきい値を `--threshold 20K` で指定しました。これは `last_block >= "
"2`のときに`REINDEX`が動くサイズです。"

msgid "### Execute query"
msgstr "### クエリの例"

msgid ""
"```sql\n"
"CREATE TABLE notes (content text);\n"
"CREATE INDEX notes_index ON notes USING pgroonga (content);\n"
"INSERT INTO notes SELECT 'NOTES' FROM generate_series(1, 200);\n"
"DELETE FROM notes;\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

msgid "Check `pgroonga_wal_status()`:"
msgstr "`pgroonga_wal_status()`の結果を確認します:"

msgid ""
"```sql\n"
"SELECT name, last_block FROM pgroonga_wal_status();\n"
"    name     | last_block \n"
"-------------+------------\n"
" notes_index |          2\n"
"(1 row)\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

msgid "### Check logs"
msgstr "### ログの確認"

msgid "#### WAL exceeds the threshold"
msgstr "#### しきい値を超えたとき"

msgid "Output the SQL to be run, the start time, and the end time."
msgstr "実行するSQL、`REINDEX` の開始時間、 `REINDEX` の終了時間を出力します。"

msgid ""
"```console\n"
"$ grep pgroonga-primary-maintainer.sh /var/log/messages\n"
"...\n"
"Jul  4 00:39:26 example pgroonga-primary-maintainer.sh[84272]: Run 'REINDEX "
"INDEX CONCURRENTLY notes_index'\n"
"Jul  4 00:39:26 example pgroonga-primary-maintainer.sh[84289]: Thu Jul  4 "
"00:39:26 UTC 2024\n"
"Jul  4 00:39:26 example pgroonga-primary-maintainer.sh[84290]: REINDEX\n"
"Jul  4 00:39:26 example pgroonga-primary-maintainer.sh[84343]: Thu Jul  4 "
"00:39:26 UTC 2024\n"
"...\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"If multiple indexes are targeted, `REINDEX` is run in sequential order,\n"
"with similar output each time."
msgstr ""
"複数のインデックスのWALのサイズがしきい値を超えていた場合は、シーケンシャル"
"に `REINDEX` を実行します。"

msgid ""
"```sql\n"
"SELECT name, last_block FROM pgroonga_wal_status();\n"
"    name     | last_block \n"
"-------------+------------\n"
" notes_index |          1\n"
"(1 row)\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

msgid "#### No WAL exceeds the threshold"
msgstr "#### しきい値を超えていないとき"

msgid "No output."
msgstr "出力はありません。"

